changeSet.sql: CREATE TABLE public.recordable ( creation_date timestamp without time zone NOT NULL, creator_id uuid NOT NULL, last_modification_date timestamp without time zone NOT NULL, last_modifier_id uuid NOT NULL, owner_id uuid NOT NULL, tag character varying );

CREATE TABLE public.base_address ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, address_line1 character varying, address_line2 character varying, company character varying, email character varying NOT NULL, phone1 character varying, phone2 character varying, state_or_province character varying, city character varying, country_id uuid NOT NULL ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.base_country ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, phone_code integer NOT NULL, code character varying NOT NULL, name character varying NOT NULL, currency_id uuid NOT NULL ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.base_currency ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, name character varying NOT NULL, after boolean NOT NULL, "precision" integer NOT NULL, symbol character varying NOT NULL, code character varying NOT NULL ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.base_event ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, information character varying NOT NULL, details character varying NOT NULL, identifier character varying NOT NULL, level character varying NOT NULL ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.base_language ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, iso_code character varying NOT NULL, code character varying NOT NULL, name character varying NOT NULL, enabled boolean NOT NULL ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.base_person ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, name character varying NOT NULL, preferred_language_id uuid NOT NULL, billing_address_id uuid NOT NULL, preferred_currency_id uuid NOT NULL, is_company boolean NOT NULL, photo character varying NOT NULL, time_zone_id character varying NOT NULL, address_id uuid NOT NULL ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.base_planned_task ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, metadata character varying NOT NULL, description character varying NOT NULL, status character varying NOT NULL, type character varying NOT NULL, start_date timestamp without time zone NOT NULL ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.base_sequence ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, step integer NOT NULL, next_number bigint NOT NULL, size integer NOT NULL, name character varying NOT NULL, prefix character varying, suffix character varying, code character varying NOT NULL ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.billing_order ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, customer_address_id uuid NOT NULL, supplier_address_id uuid NOT NULL, type character varying NOT NULL, reference character varying, publishing_date date NOT NULL, customer_id uuid NOT NULL, supplier_id uuid NOT NULL, vat_amount double precision NOT NULL, total_amount double precision NOT NULL, base_currency_id uuid NOT NULL, exchange_rate double precision NOT NULL, currency_id uuid NOT NULL, description character varying, amount double precision NOT NULL ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.billing_order_line ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, product_id uuid NOT NULL, description character varying, order_id uuid NOT NULL, unit_price double precision NOT NULL, no integer NOT NULL, name character varying NOT NULL, base_unit_price double precision NOT NULL, ht_amount double precision NOT NULL, quantity integer NOT NULL ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.billing_order_tax ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, amount double precision NOT NULL, name character varying NOT NULL, order_id uuid NOT NULL, origin_id uuid NOT NULL ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.billing_payment_method ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, password character varying, online boolean NOT NULL, username character varying, default_cashier_id uuid NOT NULL, logo character varying NOT NULL, enabled boolean NOT NULL, type character varying NOT NULL, name character varying NOT NULL ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.billing_payment_receipt ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, object character varying NOT NULL, state character varying NOT NULL, reference character varying NOT NULL, order_id uuid NOT NULL, payment_date date NOT NULL, description character varying, request_id uuid NOT NULL, metadata character varying NOT NULL, amount double precision NOT NULL, method_id uuid NOT NULL, remitter_id uuid NOT NULL, cashier_id uuid NOT NULL ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.billing_payment_request ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, amount double precision NOT NULL, metadata character varying NOT NULL, reference character varying NOT NULL, order_id uuid NOT NULL, status character varying NOT NULL, object character varying NOT NULL, notes character varying ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.billing_product ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, name character varying NOT NULL, enabled boolean NOT NULL, description character varying, price double precision NOT NULL, reference character varying NOT NULL, catalog_id uuid NOT NULL ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.billing_subscription_contract ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, invoice_id uuid, subscriber_id uuid NOT NULL, begin_date date NOT NULL, end_date date NOT NULL, purchase_order_id uuid NOT NULL ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.billing_tax ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, short_name character varying NOT NULL, value_type character varying NOT NULL, type character varying NOT NULL, value double precision NOT NULL, name character varying NOT NULL ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.membership_access_param ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, name character varying NOT NULL, access_id uuid NOT NULL, message character varying NOT NULL, default_value character varying NOT NULL, value_type character varying NOT NULL, quantifier character varying NOT NULL, code character varying NOT NULL ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.membership_plan_feature ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, description character varying, name character varying NOT NULL, no integer NOT NULL, plan_id uuid NOT NULL, enabled boolean NOT NULL, basic boolean NOT NULL ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.membership_registration_request ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, password character varying NOT NULL, name character varying NOT NULL, preferred_language_id uuid NOT NULL, dead_line timestamp without time zone NOT NULL, status character varying NOT NULL, salt character varying NOT NULL, applicant_id uuid, email character varying NOT NULL ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.membership_user ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, profile_id uuid NOT NULL, active boolean NOT NULL, salt character varying NOT NULL, password character varying NOT NULL ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.supervisor_activity ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, name character varying NOT NULL, periodicity_id uuid NOT NULL, app_owner_id uuid NOT NULL, description character varying NOT NULL, default_shown boolean NOT NULL, version character varying NOT NULL, is_template boolean NOT NULL, template_src_id uuid, tags character varying, state character varying, designer_id uuid, license character varying ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.supervisor_activity_template_published ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, profile_id uuid NOT NULL, nb_subscriptions bigint NOT NULL, nb_likes bigint NOT NULL, score double precision NOT NULL, price double precision NOT NULL, nb_paid bigint NOT NULL, icon character varying NOT NULL, availability character varying NOT NULL, nb_views bigint NOT NULL ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.supervisor_data_field ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, style character varying NOT NULL, name character varying NOT NULL, type character varying NOT NULL, code character varying NOT NULL, description character varying NOT NULL, model_id uuid NOT NULL ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.supervisor_data_field_of_sheet ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, origin_field_id uuid NOT NULL, sheet_id uuid NOT NULL, value character varying, default_value character varying, structure_id uuid, sheet_to_refer_id uuid ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.supervisor_data_link ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, name character varying NOT NULL, data_domain_definition character varying NOT NULL, indicator_id uuid NOT NULL, active boolean NOT NULL, model_id uuid NOT NULL ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.supervisor_data_model ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, description character varying NOT NULL, is_template boolean NOT NULL, active boolean NOT NULL, activity_id uuid NOT NULL, name character varying NOT NULL, interacting boolean NOT NULL, type character varying NOT NULL, code character varying NOT NULL ) INHERITS (public.recordable);
CREATE TABLE public.supervisor_data_sheet ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, date date NOT NULL, reference character varying NOT NULL, model_id uuid NOT NULL, table_id uuid ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.supervisor_dynamic_table_2_col ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, unity_symbol character varying NOT NULL, manage_evolution_percent boolean NOT NULL, nb_max_of_elements_to_show integer NOT NULL, symbol_position character varying NOT NULL, ordering_mode character varying NOT NULL ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.supervisor_editable_data_field ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, is_mandatory boolean NOT NULL, user_scope character varying NOT NULL, no integer NOT NULL, is_read_only boolean, default_value character varying, must_edit_once boolean, take_last_value boolean, structure_id uuid, order_direction character varying, nb_max_values integer, can_be_updated boolean ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.supervisor_formular_condition ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, default_value double precision NOT NULL, comparator character varying NOT NULL, param_id uuid NOT NULL, value character varying NOT NULL ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.supervisor_formular_expression ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, formular_id uuid NOT NULL, no integer NOT NULL, type character varying NOT NULL, extended_model_aggregate character varying, extended_child_aggregate character varying ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.supervisor_formular_extended_to_model_source ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, reference_id uuid NOT NULL, model_id uuid NOT NULL, expr_id uuid NOT NULL, comparator character varying NOT NULL, interacting boolean NOT NULL, active boolean NOT NULL, model_field_id uuid NOT NULL, field_to_extend_id uuid NOT NULL ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.supervisor_gauge_setting ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, minor_ticks integer NOT NULL, symbol_position character varying NOT NULL, max double precision NOT NULL, min double precision NOT NULL, gauge_type character varying NOT NULL, unity_symbol character varying NOT NULL, major_ticks integer NOT NULL ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.supervisor_gauge_zone ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, color character varying NOT NULL, max double precision NOT NULL, gauge_id uuid NOT NULL, min double precision NOT NULL ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.supervisor_indicator_general_setting ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, description character varying, col integer NOT NULL, size_x integer NOT NULL, "row" integer NOT NULL, activity_id uuid NOT NULL, single_label character varying NOT NULL, periodicity_id uuid, is_template boolean NOT NULL, type_id uuid NOT NULL, size_y integer NOT NULL, plural_label character varying NOT NULL, code character varying NOT NULL, state character varying, tags character varying, name character varying ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.supervisor_indicator_type ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, description character varying NOT NULL, name character varying NOT NULL, default_size_x integer NOT NULL, default_size_y integer NOT NULL, short_name character varying NOT NULL ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.supervisor_indicator_type_param ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, code character varying NOT NULL, type character varying NOT NULL, no integer NOT NULL, category character varying NOT NULL, name character varying NOT NULL, indicator_type_id uuid NOT NULL, predefined_values character varying ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.supervisor_list_data_field_source ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, active boolean NOT NULL, model_id uuid NOT NULL, order_field_id uuid NOT NULL, field_to_display_id uuid NOT NULL, field_id uuid NOT NULL ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.supervisor_mapped_data_field ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, field_to_use_id uuid NOT NULL, param_id uuid NOT NULL, link_id uuid NOT NULL, operator character varying NOT NULL ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.supervisor_model_filter_condition ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, field_id uuid NOT NULL, filter_id uuid NOT NULL, value character varying, comparator character varying NOT NULL ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.supervisor_periodicity ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, close_interval boolean NOT NULL, unit character varying NOT NULL, number integer NOT NULL, reference date NOT NULL ) INHERITS (public.recordable);

CREATE TABLE public.supervisor_when_case ( id uuid PRIMARY KEY, left_arg_id uuid NOT NULL, expression_id uuid NOT NULL, right_arg_id uuid, result_id uuid NOT NULL, comparator character varying NOT NULL ) INHERITS (public.recordable);
